data.description: 100% move in ready! Fully renovated in 2022, 4482 Somerton Rd offers just over 1500 sq-ft of thoughtfully laid out living space! Fully redecorated with the modern buyer in mind and all major systems, appliances and roof replaced, just unload the truck and begin your new living experience! 3 beds and 2 full baths arranged across an open floor concept. Enter to the spacious living room and immediately get the feeling of home! Eat-in fully redone kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops. stylish backsplash, gas stove, recess lighting and much more! Conveniently located 1st full bath with tub/shower combination and subway tile. Bedrooms provide good natural lighting and are equipped with ceiling fans and good closet space. The en suite bathroom has a walk in shower with subway tile and glass door. House has gas heat! The backyard is fully fenced complete with a back deck for relaxation. Gutters have all been custom fitted with leaf guards to minimize routine maintenance! This home is perfect for the first time home buyer who needs not worry about near future repairs or hassles or for the current homeowner looking to downsize into something more comfortable and cozy!
